Third Department,

August, 1975

(August 7, 1975) Schenectady Urban Renewal Agency, Respondent, v Earl M. Bucci et al., Appellants.

Motion to dismiss appeal denied, without costs (CPLR 5701, subd [a], par 2, cl [v]; see Central Hudson Gas & Elec. Co. r Newman, 35 AD2d 989). Greenblbtt, J. P., Kane, Main, Larkin and Reynolds, JJ., concur.
